jokes.setup: Why does the size of the snack not matter to a giraffe?
jokes.delivery: Because even a little bit goes a long way.

jokes.setup:
My neighbor is a 90 year old with Alzheimer's, I see him every morning and he asks me If I've seen his wife.
Every day I have to tell this poor man that his wife died 20 years ago.
I could have moved to another house or even ignore his question.
jokes.delivery: But the look of joy in his eyes whenever I answer him is worth the world.

jokes.setup: Why did the Python data scientist get arrested at customs?
jokes.delivery: She was caught trying to import pandas!

jokes.setup:
The gas Argon walks into a bar.
The barkeeper says "What would you like to drink?"
What do you call a cow with no legs?
I'm thinking of setting up a comedy group to help people going through cancer treatment.
jokes.delivery: I'll call it "A Sense of Tumor".

jokes.setup: What's the difference between a poorly dressed man on a unicycle and a well dressed man on a bicycle?
What did the customer say to the waiter?
jokes.delivery: I'm all fed up with your service.
